\v 14 e lhe <a name="00900101400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Até quando <a name="00900101400014" ll="SDBH:שׁכר:000001">estarás</a> tu <a name="00900101400014" ll="SDBH:שׁכר:000001">embriagada</a>? <a name="00900101400016" ll="SDBH:סור:000008">Aparta</a> de ti esse <a name="00900101400020" ll="SDBH:יַיִן:000000" il="Flora:2.12a;HK00108;LB00103;LB00107;vineyard1679, rp">vinho</a>! 
