\v 5 Sucedeu que, <a name="00900400500008">vindo</a> a <a name="00900400500010" ll="SDBH:אֲרֹון:000001" il="LB00283;NBGlo20140501;NBGlo20140501e;NBGlo20140509;Realia:4.1a">arca</a> da <a name="00900400500012" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000">Aliança</a> <a name="00900400500014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">do</a> <a name="00900400500014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> ao <a name="00900400500020" ll="SDBH:מַחֲנֶה:000000" il="HK00220;HK00221;HK00223;il_israel_camp_sinai;il_jordan_crossing_d01">arraial</a>, <a name="00900400500024" ll="SDBH:רוע:000000">rompeu</a> todo o <a name="00900400500028" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a> em <a name="00900400500032" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000003">grandes</a> <a name="00900400500030" ll="SDBH:תְּרוּעָה:000000" il="HK00188">brados</a>, e <a name="00900400500036" ll="SDBH:הום:000000">ressoou</a> a <a name="00900400500040" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>. 
\v 6 <a name="00900400600004">Ouvindo</a> os <a name="00900400600006" ll="SDBH:פְּלִשְׁתִּי:000000" il="il_qasile_houses;il_qasile_temple_d01">filisteus</a> a <a name="00900400600010">voz</a> do <a name="00900400600014" ll="SDBH:תְּרוּעָה:000000" il="HK00188">júbilo</a>, <a name="00900400600018" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disseram</a>: Que <a name="00900400600022">voz</a> de <a name="00900400600030" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000003">grande</a> <a name="00900400600026" ll="SDBH:תְּרוּעָה:000000" il="HK00188">júbilo</a> é esta no <a name="00900400600038" ll="SDBH:מַחֲנֶה:000000" il="HK00220;HK00221;HK00223;il_israel_camp_sinai;il_jordan_crossing_d01">arraial</a> dos <a name="00900400600042" ll="SDBH:עִבְרִי:000000">hebreus</a>? Então, <a name="00900400600046">souberam</a> que a <a name="00900400600050" ll="SDBH:אֲרֹון:000001" il="LB00283;NBGlo20140501;NBGlo20140501e;NBGlo20140509;Realia:4.1a">arca</a> do <a name="00900400600052" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> era <a name="00900400600054">vinda</a> ao <a name="00900400600060" ll="SDBH:מַחֲנֶה:000000" il="HK00220;HK00221;HK00223;il_israel_camp_sinai;il_jordan_crossing_d01">arraial</a>. 
