\v 8 <a name="00900400800002" ll="SDBH:אֹוי:000000">Ai</a> de nós! Quem <a name="00900400800008" ll="SDBH:נצל:000005">nos</a> <a name="00900400800008" ll="SDBH:נצל:000005">livrará</a> das <a name="00900400800012">mãos</a> destes <a name="00900400800020" ll="SDBH:אַדִּיר:000000">grandiosos</a> <a name="00900400800016" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000000;SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">deuses</a>? São os <a name="00900400800032" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000000;SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">deuses</a> que <a name="00900400800036" ll="SDBH:נכה:000010">feriram</a> aos <a name="00900400800040" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">egípcios</a> com toda sorte de <a name="00900400800046" ll="SDBH:מַכָּה:000000">pragas</a> no <a name="00900400800052" ll="SDBH:מִדְבָּר:000000" il="RS26447_ISR91T-418;Sinai-191;Sinai-220;Sinai-3;Sinai178;Sinai190;tb113006604">deserto</a>. 
\v 9 <a name="00900400900002" ll="SDBH:חזק:000007">Sede</a> <a name="00900400900002" ll="SDBH:חזק:000007">fortes</a>, ó <a name="00900400900012" ll="SDBH:פְּלִשְׁתִּי:000000" il="il_qasile_houses;il_qasile_temple_d01">filisteus</a>! <a name="00900400900006">Portai</a>-<a name="00900400900006">vos</a> varonilmente, para que não <a name="00900400900016" ll="SDBH:עבד:000000">venhais</a> <a name="00900400900016" ll="SDBH:עבד:000000">a</a> <a name="00900400900016" ll="SDBH:עבד:000000">ser</a> <a name="00900400900016" ll="SDBH:עבד:000000">escravos</a> dos <a name="00900400900022" ll="SDBH:עִבְרִי:000000">hebreus</a>, como eles <a name="00900400900028" ll="SDBH:עבד:000000">serviram</a> a vós outros! <a name="00900400900034">Portai</a>-<a name="00900400900034">vos</a> varonilmente e <a name="00900400900042" ll="SDBH:לחם:001001">pelejai</a>! 
