\v 13 Quando <a name="00900401300004">chegou</a>, <a name="00900401300010" ll="SDBH:עֵלִי:000000">Eli</a> estava <a name="00900401300012">assentado</a> numa <a name="00900401300018" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000000" il="Ashur-nasir-pal_II_throne;Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;adr1603194845;mb120901102">cadeira</a>, ao pé do caminho, <a name="00900401300026" ll="SDBH:צפה:000001">olhando</a> <a name="00900401300026" ll="SDBH:צפה:000001">como</a> <a name="00900401300026" ll="SDBH:צפה:000001">quem</a> <a name="00900401300026" ll="SDBH:צפה:000001">espera</a>, porque o <a name="00900401300032" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">seu</a> <a name="00900401300032" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">coração</a> estava <a name="00900401300034" ll="SDBH:חָרֵד:000000">tremendo</a> pela <a name="00900401300038" ll="SDBH:אֲרֹון:000001" il="LB00283;NBGlo20140501;NBGlo20140501e;NBGlo20140509;Realia:4.1a">arca</a> de <a name="00900401300042" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a>. Depois de <a name="00900401300050">entrar</a> o <a name="00900401300048">homem</a> na <a name="00900401300060" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a> e <a name="00900401300054" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">dar</a> <a name="00900401300054" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">as</a> <a name="00900401300054" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">novas</a>, toda a <a name="00900401300070" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a> <a name="00900401300064" ll="SDBH:זעק:000000">prorrompeu</a> <a name="00900401300064" ll="SDBH:זעק:000000">em</a> <a name="00900401300064" ll="SDBH:זעק:000000">gritos</a>. 
