\v 15 <a name="00900401500006" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000005">Era</a> <a name="00900401500004" ll="SDBH:עֵלִי:000000">Eli</a> <a name="00900401500006" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000005">da</a> <a name="00900401500006" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000005">idade</a> de <a name="00900401500008" ll="SDBH:תֵּשַׁע:000001">noventa</a> e <a name="00900401500012" ll="SDBH:שְׁמֹנֶה:000000">oito</a> <a name="00900401500014" ll="SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">anos</a>; os <a name="00900401500018" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">seus</a> <a name="00900401500018" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> <a name="00900401500020">tinham</a> <a name="00900401500020">cegado</a>, e já não <a name="00900401500026" ll="SDBH:יכל:000000">podia</a> <a name="00900401500030" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">ver</a>. 
