\v 4 Então, <a name="00900600400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disseram</a>: Qual será a <a name="00900600400010" ll="SDBH:אָשָׁם:000002">oferta</a> <a name="00900600400010" ll="SDBH:אָשָׁם:000002">pela</a> <a name="00900600400010" ll="SDBH:אָשָׁם:000002">culpa</a> que lhe <a name="00900600400014" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">havemos</a> <a name="00900600400014" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">de</a> <a name="00900600400014" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">apresentar</a>? <a name="00900600400020" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Responderam</a>: <a name="00900600400022" ll="SDBH:מִסְפָּר:000002">Segundo</a> <a name="00900600400022" ll="SDBH:מִסְפָּר:000002">o</a> <a name="00900600400022" ll="SDBH:מִסְפָּר:000002">número</a> dos <a name="00900600400024" ll="SDBH:סֶרֶן:001000">príncipes</a> dos <a name="00900600400026" ll="SDBH:פְּלִשְׁתִּי:000000" il="il_qasile_houses;il_qasile_temple_d01">filisteus</a>, <a name="00900600400028" ll="SDBH:חָמֵשׁ:000000">cinco</a> <a name="00900600400030;00900600400032" ll="SDBH:טְחֹרִים:000001;SDBH:עֹפֶל:000002">tumores</a> de <a name="00900600400034" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000000" il="Bolen00041;Bolen00050;Bolen00053;adr1006039110;adr1305240906;adr1306212575">ouro</a> e <a name="00900600400038" ll="SDBH:חָמֵשׁ:000000">cinco</a> <a name="00900600400040" ll="SDBH:עַכְבָּר:000000" il="Fauna:2.27c;Fauna:2.27e;Rattus_rattus_01">ratos</a> de <a name="00900600400042" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000000" il="Bolen00041;Bolen00050;Bolen00053;adr1006039110;adr1305240906;adr1306212575">ouro</a>, porquanto a <a name="00900600400046" ll="SDBH:מַגֵּפָה:000000">praga</a> é <a name="00900600400048" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">uma</a> e a mesma sobre todos vós e sobre todos os <a name="00900600400058" ll="SDBH:סֶרֶן:001000">vossos</a> <a name="00900600400058" ll="SDBH:סֶרֶן:001000">príncipes</a>. 
