\v 10 e <a name="00901101000004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disseram</a> aos amonitas: <a name="00901101000010" ll="SDBH:מָחָר:000000">Amanhã</a>, <a name="00901101000012" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">nos</a> <a name="00901101000012" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">entregaremos</a> a vós outros; então, nos <a name="00901101000018">fareis</a> segundo o que <a name="00901101000028" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002">melhor</a> <a name="00901101000032" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">vos</a> <a name="00901101000032" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">parecer</a>. 
\v 11 Sucedeu que, ao <a name="00901101100008" ll="SDBH:מָחֳרָת:000000">outro</a> <a name="00901101100008" ll="SDBH:מָחֳרָת:000000">dia</a>, <a name="00901101100014" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> <a name="00901101100012" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000001">dividiu</a> o <a name="00901101100020" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> em <a name="00901101100022" ll="SDBH:שָׁלֹשׁ:000000">três</a> <a name="00901101100024" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000012">companhias</a>, que, pela <a name="00901101100040" ll="SDBH:אַשְׁמֹרֶת:000000">vigília</a> da <a name="00901101100044" ll="SDBH:בֹּקֶר:000000">manhã</a>, <a name="00901101100028">vieram</a> para o <a name="00901101100032" ll="SDBH:תָּוֶךְ:000000">meio</a> do <a name="00901101100036" ll="SDBH:מַחֲנֶה:000000" il="HK00220;HK00221;HK00223;il_israel_camp_sinai;il_jordan_crossing_d01">arraial</a> e <a name="00901101100048" ll="SDBH:נכה:000004">feriram</a> a <a name="00901101100052" ll="SDBH:עַמֹּון:000000" il="Bolen00054;Satellite Bible Atlas00009;Satellite Bible Atlas00037;tb031115098;tb031115104">Amom</a>, até que se fez sentir o <a name="00901101100056" ll="SDBH:חֹם:000001">calor</a> do <a name="00901101100060" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000000">dia</a>. Os <a name="00901101100068" ll="SDBH:שׁאר:000000">sobreviventes</a> <a name="00901101100072" ll="SDBH:פוץ:000000">se</a> <a name="00901101100072" ll="SDBH:פוץ:000000">espalharam</a>, e não <a name="00901101100078" ll="SDBH:שׁאר:000000">ficaram</a> <a name="00901101100082" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a> deles <a name="00901101100084">juntos</a>.
    
\v 12 Então, <a name="00901101200004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> o <a name="00901101200008" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> a <a name="00901101200012" ll="SDBH:שְׁמוּאֵל:000000">Samuel</a>: Quem são aqueles que <a name="00901101200018" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diziam</a>: <a name="00901101200022" ll="SDBH:מלך:000000">Reinará</a> <a name="00901101200020" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> sobre nós? Trazei-os para aqui, para <a name="00901101200034" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">que</a> <a name="00901101200034" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">os</a> <a name="00901101200034" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">matemos</a>. 
