\v 5 E ele lhes <a name="00901200500004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: O <a name="00901200500010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> é <a name="00901200500008" ll="SDBH:עֵד:000000">testemunha</a> contra vós outros, e o <a name="00901200500018" ll="SDBH:מָשִׁיחַ:000000" il="Anoint">seu</a> <a name="00901200500018" ll="SDBH:מָשִׁיחַ:000000" il="Anoint">ungido</a> é, <a name="00901200500022" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000001">hoje</a>, <a name="00901200500016" ll="SDBH:עֵד:000000">testemunha</a> de que nada <a name="00901200500032;00901200500038" ll="SDBH:מְאוּמָה:000000;SDBH:מצא:000011">tendes</a> <a name="00901200500032;00901200500038" ll="SDBH:מְאוּמָה:000000;SDBH:מצא:000011">achado</a> nas <a name="00901200500036">minhas</a> <a name="00901200500036">mãos</a>. E o povo <a name="00901200500042" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">confirmou</a>: Deus é <a name="00901200500044" ll="SDBH:עֵד:000000">testemunha</a>.
    
