\v 8 <a name="00901300800008">Esperou</a> Saul <a name="00901300800010" ll="SDBH:שֶׁבַע:000000">sete</a> <a name="00901300800012" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000001">dias</a>, segundo o <a name="00901300800018" ll="SDBH:מֹועֵד:000001">prazo</a> <a name="00901300800018" ll="SDBH:מֹועֵד:000001">determinado</a> por <a name="00901300800022" ll="SDBH:שְׁמוּאֵל:000000">Samuel</a>; <a name="00901300800026;00901300800028" ll="SDBH:לֹא:000000">não</a> <a name="00901300800026;00901300800028" ll="SDBH:לֹא:000000">vindo</a>, porém, Samuel a <a name="00901300800034" ll="SDBH:גִּלְגָּל:001000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00052">Gilgal</a>, o <a name="00901300800042">povo</a> se <a name="00901300800038" ll="SDBH:פוץ:000002">foi</a> <a name="00901300800038" ll="SDBH:פוץ:000002">espalhando</a> dali. 
