\v 24 Então, <a name="00901502400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> <a name="00901502400006" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> a <a name="00901502400010" ll="SDBH:שְׁמוּאֵל:000000">Samuel</a>: <a name="00901502400012" ll="SDBH:חטא:001005">Pequei</a>, pois <a name="00901502400016">transgredi</a> o <a name="00901502400020" ll="SDBH:פֶּה:000001">mandamento</a> <a name="00901502400022" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">do</a> <a name="00901502400022" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> e as <a name="00901502400028" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">tuas</a> <a name="00901502400028" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavras</a>; porque <a name="00901502400032" ll="SDBH:ירא:000000">temi</a> o <a name="00901502400038" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> e <a name="00901502400042">dei</a> <a name="00901502400042">ouvidos</a> à <a name="00901502400046">sua</a> <a name="00901502400046">voz</a>. 
