\v 5 <a name="00901800500004" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">Saía</a> <a name="00901800500006" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> aonde quer que <a name="00901800500016" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> <a name="00901800500014" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">o</a> <a name="00901800500014" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">enviava</a> e <a name="00901800500018" ll="SDBH:שׂכל:000000">se</a> <a name="00901800500018" ll="SDBH:שׂכל:000000">conduzia</a> <a name="00901800500018" ll="SDBH:שׂכל:000000">com</a> <a name="00901800500018" ll="SDBH:שׂכל:000000">prudência</a>; de modo que <a name="00901800500024" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> <a name="00901800500022" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000019">o</a> <a name="00901800500022" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000019">pôs</a> sobre <a name="00901800500028;00901800500032" ll="SDBH:מִלְחָמָה:000002">tropas</a> do <a name="00901800500028;00901800500032" ll="SDBH:מִלְחָמָה:000002">seu</a> <a name="00901800500028;00901800500032" ll="SDBH:מִלְחָמָה:000002">exército</a>, e era ele <a name="00901800500036" ll="SDBH:יטב:000006">benquisto</a> <a name="00901800500040" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">de</a> todo o <a name="00901800500046" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> e até <a name="00901800500054" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">dos</a> próprios <a name="00901800500056" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servos</a> de <a name="00901800500058" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>.
    
