\v 20 Mas <a name="00901802000006" ll="SDBH:מִיכַל:000000">Mical</a>, a outra <a name="00901802000008" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000000">filha</a> de <a name="00901802000010" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>, <a name="00901802000004" ll="SDBH:אהב:000000">amava</a> a <a name="00901802000014" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>. <a name="00901802000018" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">Contaram</a>-no a <a name="00901802000022" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>, e <a name="00901802000030" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">isso</a> <a name="00901802000026;00901802000034" ll="SDBH:ישׁר:000008;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">lhe</a> <a name="00901802000026;00901802000034" ll="SDBH:ישׁר:000008;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">agradou</a>. 
