\v 21 <a name="00901902100004" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">Avisado</a> disto, <a name="00901902100008" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> <a name="00901902100012" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">enviou</a> <a name="00901902100016" ll="SDBH:אַחֵר:000000">outros</a> <a name="00901902100014" ll="SDBH:מַלְאָךְ:000000">mensageiros</a>, e também estes <a name="00901902100020" ll="SDBH:נבא:000000">profetizaram</a>; então, <a name="00901902100034" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">enviou</a> <a name="00901902100030" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> <a name="00901902100028">ainda</a> <a name="00901902100036" ll="SDBH:מַלְאָךְ:000000">uns</a> <a name="00901902100038" ll="SDBH:שְׁלִישִׁי:000000">terceiros</a>, os quais também <a name="00901902100042" ll="SDBH:נבא:000000">profetizaram</a>. 
