\v 4 (3) <a name="00902400400004">Chegou</a> a uns <a name="00902400400008" ll="SDBH:גְּדֵרָה:000001" il="NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1">currais</a> de <a name="00902400400012" ll="SDBH:צֹאן:000000" il="LB00012;LB00015;LB00017;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;NBGpb20140401b;Realia:1.2.1;tb111706002">ovelhas</a> no <a name="00902400400018" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000000">caminho</a>, onde havia uma <a name="00902400400024" ll="SDBH:מְעָרָה:000000">caverna</a>; <a name="00902400400028">entrou</a> nela <a name="00902400400030" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>, a <a name="00902400400034;00902400400038" ll="SDBH:סכך:000002;SDBH:רֶגֶל:000007">aliviar</a> <a name="00902400400034;00902400400038" ll="SDBH:סכך:000002;SDBH:רֶגֶל:000007">o</a> <a name="00902400400034;00902400400038" ll="SDBH:סכך:000002;SDBH:רֶגֶל:000007">ventre</a>. Ora, <a name="00902400400042" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> e os seus homens estavam <a name="00902400400056" ll="SDBH:ישׁב:000000">assentados</a> no <a name="00902400400050" ll="SDBH:יְרֵכָה:000000">mais</a> <a name="00902400400050" ll="SDBH:יְרֵכָה:000000">interior</a> da <a name="00902400400054" ll="SDBH:מְעָרָה:000000">mesma</a>. 
