\v 6 (5) Sucedeu, porém, que, <a name="00902400600006" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:002001">depois</a>, <a name="00902400600012" ll="SDBH:נכה:000011">sentiu</a> <a name="00902400600016" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> <a name="00902400600012" ll="SDBH:נכה:000011">bater</a>-lhe o <a name="00902400600014" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">coração</a>, por ter <a name="00902400600024" ll="SDBH:כרת:000000">cortado</a> a <a name="00902400600028" ll="SDBH:כָּנָף:000001" il="Realia:6.2">orla</a> <a name="00902400600028" ll="SDBH:כָּנָף:000001" il="Realia:6.2">do</a> <a name="00902400600028" ll="SDBH:כָּנָף:000001" il="Realia:6.2">manto</a> de <a name="00902400600034" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>; 
\v 7 (6) e <a name="00902400700004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> aos seus homens: O <a name="00902400700016" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> me <a name="00902400700010" ll="SDBH:חֲלִילָה:000000">guarde</a> de que <a name="00902400700020">eu</a> <a name="00902400700020">faça</a> tal <a name="00902400700026" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">coisa</a> ao <a name="00902400700034" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">meu</a> <a name="00902400700034" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">senhor</a>, isto é, que eu <a name="00902400700044" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000015">estenda</a> <a name="00902400700046">a</a> <a name="00902400700046">mão</a> contra ele, pois é o <a name="00902400700038;00902400700052" ll="SDBH:מָשִׁיחַ:000000" il="Anoint">ungido</a> do <a name="00902400700040;00902400700054" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>. 
\v 8 (7) Com estas <a name="00902400800016" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavras</a>, <a name="00902400800006" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> <a name="00902400800004" ll="SDBH:שׁסע:000002">conteve</a> os seus homens e não <a name="00902400800022">lhes</a> <a name="00902400800022">permitiu</a> que <a name="00902400800026">se</a> <a name="00902400800026">levantassem</a> contra <a name="00902400800030" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>; <a name="00902400800036">retirando</a>-<a name="00902400800036">se</a> <a name="00902400800034" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> da <a name="00902400800042" ll="SDBH:מְעָרָה:000000">caverna</a>, <a name="00902400800046" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">prosseguiu</a> o seu <a name="00902400800052" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000003">caminho</a>.
    
\v 9 (8) <a name="00902400900008" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:002001">Depois</a>, também <a name="00902400900006" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> <a name="00902400900004">se</a> <a name="00902400900004">levantou</a> e, <a name="00902400900014" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">saindo</a> da <a name="00902400900026" ll="SDBH:מְעָרָה:000000">caverna</a>, <a name="00902400900030" ll="SDBH:קרא:000000">gritou</a> a <a name="00902400900034" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>, <a name="00902400900038" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: Ó <a name="00902400900044" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>, <a name="00902400900040" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">meu</a> <a name="00902400900040" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">senhor</a>! <a name="00902400900048">Olhando</a> <a name="00902400900050" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> para trás, <a name="00902400900066" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">inclinou</a>-<a name="00902400900066" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">se</a> <a name="00902400900058" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> e <a name="00902400900056" ll="SDBH:קדד:000000">fez</a>-lhe <a name="00902400900056" ll="SDBH:קדד:000000">reverência</a>, com o <a name="00902400900060" ll="SDBH:אַף:000002">rosto</a> em <a name="00902400900062" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>. 
\v 10 (9) <a name="00902401000004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a> <a name="00902401000006" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> a <a name="00902401000010" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a>: <a name="00902401000012">Por</a> <a name="00902401000012">que</a> <a name="00902401000014">dás</a> tu <a name="00902401000014">ouvidos</a> às <a name="00902401000018" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavras</a> dos <a name="00902401000020" ll="SDBH:אָדָם:000000">homens</a> que <a name="00902401000024" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizem</a>: <a name="00902401000028" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> procura <a name="00902401000032" ll="SDBH:רָעָה:000002">fazer</a>-<a name="00902401000032" ll="SDBH:רָעָה:000002">te</a> <a name="00902401000032" ll="SDBH:רָעָה:000002">mal</a>? 
\v 11 (10) Os <a name="00902401100014" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">teus</a> próprios <a name="00902401100014" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> <a name="00902401100012" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">viram</a>, <a name="00902401100006" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000001">hoje</a>, que o <a name="00902401100022" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="00902401100020">te</a> <a name="00902401100020">pôs</a> em <a name="00902401100030">minhas</a> <a name="00902401100030">mãos</a> nesta <a name="00902401100036" ll="SDBH:מְעָרָה:000000">caverna</a>, e alguns <a name="00902401100040" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000" tl="HOTTP1082">disseram</a> que eu <a name="00902401100044" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">te</a> <a name="00902401100044" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">matasse</a>; porém a minha mão te <a name="00902401100048" ll="SDBH:חוס:000000">poupou</a>; porque <a name="00902401100054" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Não <a name="00902401100058" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000015">estenderei</a> a <a name="00902401100060">mão</a> contra o <a name="00902401100064" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">meu</a> <a name="00902401100064" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">senhor</a>, pois é o <a name="00902401100068" ll="SDBH:מָשִׁיחַ:000000" il="Anoint">ungido</a> de <a name="00902401100070" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Deus</a>. 
\v 12 (11) <a name="00902401200006" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">Olha</a>, pois, <a name="00902401200004" ll="SDBH:אָב:000012">meu</a> <a name="00902401200004" ll="SDBH:אָב:000012">pai</a>, <a name="00902401200010" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">vê</a> aqui a <a name="00902401200014" ll="SDBH:כָּנָף:000001" il="Realia:6.2">orla</a> do <a name="00902401200016" ll="SDBH:מְעִיל:000000" il="Realia:6.2">teu</a> <a name="00902401200016" ll="SDBH:מְעִיל:000000" il="Realia:6.2">manto</a> na <a name="00902401200020">minha</a> <a name="00902401200020">mão</a>. No fato de <a name="00902401200026" ll="SDBH:כרת:000000">haver</a> eu <a name="00902401200026" ll="SDBH:כרת:000000">cortado</a> a <a name="00902401200030" ll="SDBH:כָּנָף:000001" il="Realia:6.2">orla</a> do <a name="00902401200032" ll="SDBH:מְעִיל:000000" il="Realia:6.2">teu</a> <a name="00902401200032" ll="SDBH:מְעִיל:000000" il="Realia:6.2">manto</a> sem <a name="00902401200038" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">te</a> <a name="00902401200038" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">matar</a>, <a name="00902401200040">reconhece</a> e <a name="00902401200044" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">vê</a> que <a name="00902401200048">não</a> <a name="00902401200048">há</a> em <a name="00902401200052">mim</a> nem <a name="00902401200054" ll="SDBH:רָעָה:000000">mal</a> nem <a name="00902401200058" ll="SDBH:פֶּשַׁע:000000">rebeldia</a>, e não <a name="00902401200064" ll="SDBH:חטא:001005">pequei</a> contra ti, ainda que andas <a name="00902401200072" ll="SDBH:צדה:000000">à</a> <a name="00902401200072" ll="SDBH:צדה:000000">caça</a> da <a name="00902401200076" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">minha</a> <a name="00902401200076" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">vida</a> para <a name="00902401200080" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">ma</a> <a name="00902401200080" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">tirares</a>. 
\v 13 (12) <a name="00902401300002" ll="SDBH:שׁפט:000001" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor">Julgue</a> o <a name="00902401300004" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> entre mim e ti e <a name="00902401300014" ll="SDBH:נקם:000000">vingue</a>-<a name="00902401300014" ll="SDBH:נקם:000000">me</a> o <a name="00902401300016" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> a teu respeito; porém a <a name="00902401300022">minha</a> <a name="00902401300022">mão</a> não será contra ti. 
\v 14 (13) Dos perversos <a name="00902401400018" ll="SDBH:יצא:000025">procede</a> a <a name="00902401400020" ll="SDBH:רֶשַׁע:000001">perversidade</a>, <a name="00902401400006" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="00902401400008" ll="SDBH:מָשָׁל:000000">provérbio</a> dos <a name="00902401400012" ll="SDBH:קַדְמֹנִי:000002">antigos</a>; porém a <a name="00902401400024">minha</a> <a name="00902401400024">mão</a> não está contra ti. 
\v 15 (14) <a name="00902401500002" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001000">Após</a> quem <a name="00902401500006" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">saiu</a> o <a name="00902401500008" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> de <a name="00902401500010" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>? A quem <a name="00902401500012;00902401500018" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001000;SDBH:רדף:000000">persegue</a>? A um <a name="00902401500022" ll="SDBH:כֶּלֶב:000000" il="BK00043;Fauna:2.12b">cão</a> <a name="00902401500024" ll="SDBH:מות:000000">morto</a>? A <a name="00902401500030" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">uma</a> <a name="00902401500028" ll="SDBH:פַּרְעֹשׁ:000000" il="Fauna:6.3">pulga</a>? 
