\v 19 (18) <a name="00902401900010" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000" tl="HOTTP1083">Mostraste</a>, <a name="00902401900014" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000005">hoje</a>, que me <a name="00902401900020">fizeste</a> <a name="00902401900024" ll="SDBH:טֹובָה:000002">bem</a>; pois o <a name="00902401900032">Senhor</a> <a name="00902401900030" ll="SDBH:סגר:000004">me</a> <a name="00902401900030" ll="SDBH:סגר:000004">havia</a> <a name="00902401900030" ll="SDBH:סגר:000004">posto</a> em <a name="00902401900036">tuas</a> <a name="00902401900036">mãos</a>, e tu <a name="00902401900042">me</a> não <a name="00902401900042">mataste</a>. 
\v 20 (19) Porque <a name="00902402000008">quem</a> há que, <a name="00902402000006" ll="SDBH:מצא:000012">encontrando</a> o <a name="00902402000012" ll="SDBH:איב:000001">inimigo</a>, <a name="00902402000016" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">o</a> <a name="00902402000016" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">deixa</a> <a name="00902402000016" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">ir</a> por <a name="00902402000022" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002">bom</a> <a name="00902402000020" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000007">caminho</a>? O <a name="00902402000026" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, pois, <a name="00902402000028" ll="SDBH:שׁלם:000007">te</a> <a name="00902402000028" ll="SDBH:שׁלם:000007">pague</a> com <a name="00902402000030" ll="SDBH:טֹובָה:000001">bem</a>, pelo que, <a name="00902402000036" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000001">hoje</a>, me <a name="00902402000044">fizeste</a>. 
\v 21 (20) Agora, pois, <a name="00902402100008">tenho</a> <a name="00902402100008">certeza</a> de que serás rei e de que o <a name="00902402100024">reino</a> de <a name="00902402100026" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a> <a name="00902402100018">há</a> <a name="00902402100018">de</a> <a name="00902402100018">ser</a> <a name="00902402100018">firme</a> na <a name="00902402100022">tua</a> <a name="00902402100022">mão</a>. 
