\v 12 Então, os <a name="00902501200006" ll="SDBH:נַעַר:000000">moços</a> <a name="00902501200008" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">de</a> <a name="00902501200008" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> <a name="00902501200004" ll="SDBH:הפך:000000">puseram</a>-se a <a name="00902501200012" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000003">caminho</a>, <a name="00902501200016" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023">voltaram</a> e, <a name="00902501200020">tendo</a> <a name="00902501200020">chegado</a>, lhe <a name="00902501200024" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">contaram</a> tudo, segundo todas estas <a name="00902501200034" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavras</a>. 
