\v 36 <a name="00902503600004">Voltou</a> <a name="00902503600006" ll="SDBH:אֲבִיגַיִל:000000">Abigail</a> a <a name="00902503600010" ll="SDBH:נָבָל:001000">Nabal</a>. Eis que ele fazia em <a name="00902503600022" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">casa</a> um <a name="00902503600018" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁתֶּה:000001">banquete</a>, como <a name="00902503600026" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁתֶּה:000001">banquete</a> de <a name="00902503600030" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>; o <a name="00902503600036" ll="SDBH:נָבָל:001000">seu</a> <a name="00902503600034" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">coração</a> estava <a name="00902503600038" ll="SDBH:טוב:000000">alegre</a>, e ele, já <a name="00902503600050" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">mui</a> <a name="00902503600046" ll="SDBH:שִׁכֹּור:000000">embriagado</a>, pelo que não lhe <a name="00902503600056" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">referiu</a> ela <a name="00902503600060" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">coisa</a> <a name="00902503600060" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">alguma</a>, nem <a name="00902503600062" ll="SDBH:קָטֹן:000003">pouco</a> nem <a name="00902503600066" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000003">muito</a>, até ao <a name="00902503600070;00902503600074" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000;SDBH:אור:000004;SDBH:בֹּקֶר:000000">amanhecer</a>. 
