\v 11 <a name="00902701100014" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> não <a name="00902701100012" ll="SDBH:חיה:000002">deixava</a> <a name="00902701100012" ll="SDBH:חיה:000002">com</a> <a name="00902701100012" ll="SDBH:חיה:000002">vida</a> nem <a name="00902701100004">homem</a> nem <a name="00902701100008" ll="SDBH:אִשָּׁה:000002">mulher</a>, para os <a name="00902701100018">trazer</a> a <a name="00902701100020" ll="SDBH:גַּת:001000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00002;Satellite Bible Atlas00003;Satellite Bible Atlas00013;adr08072471511">Gate</a>, pois <a name="00902701100024" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizia</a>: Para que não nos <a name="00902701100028" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">denunciem</a>, <a name="00902701100034" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: Assim <a name="00902701100040" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> o <a name="00902701100038">fazia</a>. Este era o <a name="00902701100046" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000005">seu</a> <a name="00902701100046" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000005">proceder</a> por todos os <a name="00902701100052" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">dias</a> que <a name="00902701100056">habitou</a> na <a name="00902701100060" ll="SDBH:שָׂדֶה:000002">terra</a> dos <a name="00902701100062" ll="SDBH:פְּלִשְׁתִּי:000000" il="il_qasile_houses;il_qasile_temple_d01">filisteus</a>. 
