\v 3 Já <a name="00902800300004" ll="SDBH:שְׁמוּאֵל:000000">Samuel</a> era <a name="00902800300006" ll="SDBH:מות:000000">morto</a>, e todo o <a name="00902800300016" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a> o <a name="00902800300010" ll="SDBH:ספד:000000">tinha</a> <a name="00902800300010" ll="SDBH:ספד:000000">chorado</a> e <a name="00902800300020" ll="SDBH:קבר:000000" il="Bolen00090;Tombs-rock-cut;tb110800210">o</a> <a name="00902800300020" ll="SDBH:קבר:000000" il="Bolen00090;Tombs-rock-cut;tb110800210">tinha</a> <a name="00902800300020" ll="SDBH:קבר:000000" il="Bolen00090;Tombs-rock-cut;tb110800210">sepultado</a> em <a name="00902800300026" ll="SDBH:רָמָה:001001" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00051">Ramá</a>, que era a <a name="00902800300032" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">sua</a> <a name="00902800300032" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a>; <a name="00902800300036" ll="SDBH:שָׁאוּל:000000">Saul</a> <a name="00902800300038;00902800300056" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000;SDBH:סור:000006">havia</a> <a name="00902800300038;00902800300056" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000;SDBH:סור:000006">desterrado</a> os <a name="00902800300042" ll="SDBH:אֹוב:001001">médiuns</a> e os <a name="00902800300050" ll="SDBH:יִדְּעֹנִי:000001">adivinhos</a>. 
