\v 9 <a name="00902900900004" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">Respondeu</a>, porém, <a name="00902900900006" ll="SDBH:אָכִישׁ:000000">Aquis</a> e <a name="00902900900010" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> a <a name="00902900900014" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>: <a name="00902900900016">Bem</a> <a name="00902900900016">o</a> <a name="00902900900016">sei</a>; e que, na verdade, aos <a name="00902900900026" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">meus</a> <a name="00902900900026" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> és <a name="00902900900020" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000001">bom</a> como um <a name="00902900900030" ll="SDBH:מַלְאָךְ:000000">anjo</a> de <a name="00902900900032" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a>; porém os <a name="00902900900036" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">príncipes</a> dos <a name="00902900900038" ll="SDBH:פְּלִשְׁתִּי:000000" il="il_qasile_houses;il_qasile_temple_d01">filisteus</a> <a name="00902900900040" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disseram</a>: Não <a name="00902900900044" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">suba</a> <a name="00902900900044" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">este</a> conosco à <a name="00902900900052" ll="SDBH:מִלְחָמָה:000000">batalha</a>. 
