\v 31 aos de <a name="00903003100010" ll="SDBH:חֶבְרֹון:000000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00054">Hebrom</a> e a todos os <a name="00903003100020" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">lugares</a> em que <a name="00903003100024" ll="SDBH:הלך:000002">andara</a> <a name="00903003100028" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, ele e os seus homens.
\c 31
\v 1 Entretanto, os <a name="00903100100004" ll="SDBH:פְּלִשְׁתִּי:000000" il="il_qasile_houses;il_qasile_temple_d01">filisteus</a> <a name="00903100100006" ll="SDBH:לחם:001001">pelejaram</a> contra <a name="00903100100010" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>, e, <a name="00903100100014" ll="SDBH:נוס:000000">tendo</a> os homens de <a name="00903100100018" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a> <a name="00903100100014" ll="SDBH:נוס:000000">fugido</a> de <a name="00903100100022">diante</a> dos <a name="00903100100024" ll="SDBH:פְּלִשְׁתִּי:000000" il="il_qasile_houses;il_qasile_temple_d01">filisteus</a>, <a name="00903100100028" ll="SDBH:נפל:000038">caíram</a> <a name="00903100100030" ll="SDBH:חָלָל:000000">feridos</a> no <a name="00903100100034" ll="SDBH:הַר:000000">monte</a> <a name="00903100100038" ll="SDBH:גִּלְבֹּעַ:000000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00052;tb121704016">Gilboa</a>. 
